


* pawns should not be able to jump through other pieces, as in:
♜   ♝     ♝ ♞ ♜
♟ ♟ ♟   ♛ ♟ ♟ ♟

  ♛   ♟   ♚
      ♟   ♟
  ♚   ♞
♟ ♟ ♟   ♟   ♟ ♟
♜ ♞ ♝     ♝ ♞ ♜

It is White's turn

the pawn behind the white king is able to jump over him to save him from the
black king. He should not be able to.
